ActForeign Missions and International Organizations Act
SubjectCanada's 2025 G7 Presidency Privileges and Immunities Order
PrecisCANADA'S 2025 G7 PRESIDENCY PRIVILEGES AND IMMUNITIES ORDER in order to grant certain privileges and immunities to the following participants who will be attending the G7 Meetings: representatives of foreign state, heads of international organizations, as well as their alternates and other senior officials of an international organization, other officials of an international organization and experts who perform missions for an international organization.
RegistrationRegistration: SOR/ 2025-0042 Publication Date: 2025-03-12
